35
00:05:43,608 --> 00:05:45,259
Ah, fuck.

36
00:05:47,849 --> 00:05:49,738
Aw, fuck.

37
00:05:54,890 --> 00:05:56,415
Watch the language, everyone.

38
00:05:56,530 --> 00:06:00,660
Gents only in the bar.
Ladies' lounge is through the door.

39
00:06:00,770 --> 00:06:04,901
Yes, we don't want a drink.
We just want a taxi, if there is one.

40
00:06:05,011 --> 00:06:07,855
- Reg is at a funeral.
