69
00:10:12,362 --> 00:10:17,323
You must be Mr Lindsay.
Lindsay Campion, my wife Norman.

70
00:10:17,442 --> 00:10:20,605
- Estella.
- Just out from England?

71
00:10:20,722 --> 00:10:23,374
That's it. We arrived
just a couple of weeks ago.

72
00:10:23,483 --> 00:10:25,690
So they weren't game to send a local?

73
00:10:25,803 --> 00:10:28,090
Well, you...
you're exactly on our way.

74
00:10:29,204 --> 00:10:32,651
Oh, well. I'm glad
you got here in one piece.

75
00:10:32,764 --> 00:10:35,244
Excuse me, I gotta get back to work.

76
00:10:35,364 --> 00:10:39,290
