85
00:11:17,890 --> 00:11:19,653
Whereabouts is the, uh...

86
00:11:20,330 --> 00:11:22,139
Take him out to the thunder box.

87
00:11:23,410 --> 00:11:25,061
Just a tick.

88
00:11:28,091 --> 00:11:30,662
