162
00:16:24,567 --> 00:16:26,457
Have you seen those fairies lately?

163
00:16:26,568 --> 00:16:29,617
A couple of them were out
last Friday.

164
00:16:29,728 --> 00:16:31,776
- They were not!
- They were too.

165
00:16:31,888 --> 00:16:34,459
