- What's the time?

215
00:22:17,811 --> 00:22:21,054
The train doesn't leave until 12.

216
00:22:21,171 --> 00:22:22,503
All right.

217
00:22:29,332 --> 00:22:31,255
Anthony.

218
00:22:31,372 --> 00:22:34,342
What'd you do to him?
He's exhausted.

219
00:22:34,453 --> 00:22:37,537
- Anthony!
- Don't wake him up.

220
00:22:37,654 --> 00:22:39,895
Well, he might be dreaming.

221
00:22:40,014 --> 00:22:43,257
It's dangerous to wake somebody up
if they're dreaming

222
00:22:43,374 --> 00:22:46,218
because you leave part
of your brain behind.

223
00:22:46,334 --> 00:22:48,941
