you go feeble in the head.

224
00:22:49,055 --> 00:22:52,423
Yeah. You're living proof.

225
00:22:55,295 --> 00:22:58,106
All right, I'll join you in a minute.

226
00:23:21,739 --> 00:23:24,060
- Are you rich?
- Not very.

227
00:23:25,820 --> 00:23:29,461
- What does your father do for crust?
- Why do you ask?

228
00:23:29,580 --> 00:23:33,585
Well, Pru thinks you're bourgeois,
that's all.

229
00:23:33,700 --> 00:23:35,783
Mine was taken by a shark.

230
00:23:35,901 --> 00:23:37,824
God, how awful!

231
00:23:39,181 --> 00:23:40,990
